    <item>
      <title>美联储影响亚洲市场人气，印度卢比跌至历史低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/indian-rupee-falls-to-record-low-as-fed-weighs-on-asia-sentiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储的强硬言论影响市场人气，印度卢比兑美元汇率跌破 85，创下新低，与大多数亚洲货币一样下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/indian-rupee-falls-to-record-low-as-fed-weighs-on-asia-sentiment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 03:42:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林德：市场对美联储“反应过度”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-19/blinder-markets-overreacted-to-fed-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[普林斯顿大学经济学教授、前美联储副主席艾伦·布林德表示，他认为市场应该将美联储的信息解读为“略带鹰派色彩”。他在“彭博社：中国秀”节目中与大卫·英格尔斯和安娜贝尔·德鲁勒斯进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-19/blinder-markets-overreacted-to-fed-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 03:20:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国煤炭过剩将进一步压低煤炭价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/a-glut-of-coal-in-china-is-set-to-push-falling-prices-even-lower</link>
      <description><![CDATA[冬季来临，中国煤炭产量激增，远远超过需求，导致库存增加、价格暴跌，分析师预测价格还会进一步下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/a-glut-of-coal-in-china-is-set-to-push-falling-prices-even-lower</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 03:08:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行维持利率不变，日元兑美元跌破 155 关键水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/yen-weakens-past-155-against-dollar-after-boj-stands-pat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行维持利率不变后，日元兑美元汇率跌破155的关键水平。日本股票和债券期货继续走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/yen-weakens-past-155-against-dollar-after-boj-stands-pat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 02:56:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的 Taw 表示，“美国例外主义”将在 2025 年继续存在</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-19/timothy-taw-on-the-china-show-12-19-asia-markets-wrap-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德的托马斯·托表示，“美国例外论”预计明年将继续，但投资者正在关注美国股市的驱动因素。托在彭博电视台讨论了他对 2025 年的展望。

（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-19/timothy-taw-on-the-china-show-12-19-asia-markets-wrap-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 02:42:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电池制造商 CATL 考虑在香港上市，募资 50 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/catl-is-said-to-consider-hk-listing-to-raise-at-least-5-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，宁德时代科技股份有限公司正考虑在香港进行第二次上市，可能募集至少 50 亿美元资金，这将是自 2021 年初以来香港规模最大的一次上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/catl-is-said-to-consider-hk-listing-to-raise-at-least-5-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 02:05:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储迫使亚洲做出选择：接受货币贬值或抵制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/asian-currencies-tumble-as-fed-s-hawkish-cut-jolts-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储采取强硬降息措施后，亚洲各国央行都面临着艰难的决定 — — 是采取代价高昂的措施反击美元走强，还是袖手旁观，看着本国货币贬值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/asian-currencies-tumble-as-fed-s-hawkish-cut-jolts-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 01:12:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储预期降息次数减少，美元飙升，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-19</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预期美联储明年将减少降息，美元上涨，导致油价下跌。]]></description>
