    </item>
    <item>
      <title>违约的中国开发商佳兆业寻求法院批准对重组计划进行表决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/kaisa-seeks-court-nod-to-hold-vote-on-its-restructuring-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港一家法院批准违约的中国开发商佳兆业集团控股有限公司召开债权人会议，就其 130 亿美元的境外重组计划进行投票，制裁听证会定于 3 月 21 日举行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/kaisa-seeks-court-nod-to-hold-vote-on-its-restructuring-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市回落；日元下跌，日本央行按兵不动：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储预测明年降息次数减少，亚洲股市周四下跌。日本央行未提高借贷成本，日元下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 22:59:17 GMT</pubDate>
